text.paragraph: This is a super operator defined for Check Pathological Q in Lateral Leads in ECG diagnosis, with pre-deined input ports and outpot ports.
The input Model port receives the step model.

inputPorts.port: Input port for the step model. This operator will add its inner process to this step.
